reasoning: Muscular VSDs account for ~5-20% of all VSDs. Using overall VSD incidence of ~2.2 per 1000 live births (~220 per 100k births), muscular VSDs estimated at ~0.45 per 1000 births or ~45 per 100k. Expressed as births rather than person-years due to congenital nature of condition.
source: Birth defect surveillance registries (CDC, EUROCAT) and cardiac epidemiological studies
